span begin="00:23.156" end="00:23.326">very</span><span begin="00:23.326" end="00:23.895">thing</span> <span begin="00:23.895" end="00:24.216">just</span> <span begin="00:24.216" end="00:24.393">looks</span> <span begin="00:24.393" end="00:24.841">beau</span><span begin="00:24.841" end="00:25.023">ti</span><span begin="00:25.023" end="00:25.446">ful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一切皆美得令人心安</span></p><p begin="00:26.360" end="00:27.293" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:26.360" end="00:26.475">It's</span> <span begin="00:26.475" end="00:26.713">o</span><span begin="00:26.713" end="00:27.293">kay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无妨</span></p><p begin="00:28.220" end="00:30.938" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:28.220" end="00:28.360">The</span> <span begin="00:28.360" end="00:28.740">sun</span><span begin="00:28.740" end="00:29.173">shine</span> <span begin="00:29.173" end="00:29.863">keeps</span> <span begin="00:29.863" end="00:30.548">fal</span><span begin="00:30.548" end="00:30.938">ling</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">暖阳倾泻不息</span></p><p begin="00:33.102" end="00:39.113" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:33.102" end="00:33.232">Lone</span><span begin="00:33.232" end="00:33.452">li</span><span begin="00:33.452" end="00:34.032">ness</span> <span begin="00:34.751" end="00:34.919">does</span><span begin="00:34.919" end="00:35.136">n't</span> <span begin="00:35.136" end="00:36.586">stay</span> <span begin="00:36.586" end="00:37.368">for</span> <span begin="00:37.368" end="00:39.113">long</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">孤寂从不长驻</span></p><p begin="00:39.828" end="00:43.807" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:39.828" end="00:39.943">E</span><span begin="00:39.943" end="00:40.138">very</span><span begin="00:40.138" end="00:41.196">thing</span> <span begin="00:41.196" end="00:42.063">just</span> <span begin="00:42.063" end="00:42.937">looks</span> <span begin="00:42.937" end="00:43.355">beau</span><span begin="00:43.355" end="00:43.519">ti</span><span begin="00:43.519" end="00:43.807">ful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一切皆美得令人心安</span></p><p begin="00:48.809" end="00:50.611" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:48.809" end="00:48.972">I</span> <span begin="00:48.972" end="00:49.172">just</span> <span begin="00:49.172" end="00:49.379">want</span> <span begin="00:49.379" end="00:49.829">you</span> <span begin="00:49.829" end="00:50.019">to</span> <span begin="00:50.019" end="00:50.209">be</span> <span begin="00:50.209" end="00:50.611">happy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">惟愿你，喜乐无忧</span></p><p begin="01:30.369" end="01:30.984" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:30.369" end="01:30.495">I'm</span> <span begin="01:30.495" end="01:30.984">fine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我仍安好</span></p><p begin="01:32.030" end="01:33.807" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:32.030" end="01:32.174">The</span> <span begin="01:32.174" end="01:32.692">sky</span> <span begin="01:32.692" end="01:32.997">is</span> <span begin="01:32.997" end="01:33.422">glo</span><span begin="01:33.422" end="01:33.807">wing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">天际正流转微光</span></p><p begin="01:36.377" end="01:39.313" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:36.377" end="01:36.542">I</span> <span begin="01:36.542" end="01:36.745">guess</span> <span begin="01:36.745" end="01:36.960">it's</span> <span begin="01:36.960" end="01:37.164">e</span><span begin="01:37.164" end="01:37.851">nough</span> <span begin="01:37.851" end="01:38.021">to</span> <span begin="01:38.021" end="01:38.471">breathe</span> <span begin="01:38.471" end="01:38.839">like</span> <span begin="01:38.839" end="01:39.313">this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或许，能如此呼吸，便已足够</span></p><p begin="01:40.154" end="01:42.689" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:40.154" end="01:40.344">E</span><span begin="01:40.344" end="01:40.536">very</span><span begin="01:40.536" end="01:41.239">thing</span> <span begin="01:41.239" end="01:41.377">just</span> <span begin="01:41.377" end="01:41.587">looks</span> <span begin="01:41.587" end="01:41.987">beau</span><span begin="01:41.987" end="01:42.190">ti</span><span begin="01:42.190" end="01:42.689">ful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一切皆美得令人心安</span></p><p begin="01:43.554" end="01:44.548" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:43.554" end="01:43.670">It's</span> <span begin="01:43.670" end="01:43.887">o</span><span begin="01:43.887" end="01:44.548">kay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无妨</span></p><p begin="01:45.357" end="01:48.309" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:45.357" end="01:45.564">The</span> <span begin="01:45.564" end="01:46.017">wind</span> <span begin="01:46.017" end="01:46.360">moves</span> <span begin="01:46.360" end="01:47.009">through</span> <span begin="01:47.009" end="01:47.647">the</span> <span begin="01:47.647" end="01:48.309">trees</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">微风轻拂林梢</span></p><p begin="01:50.164" end="01:55.817" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:50.164" end="01:50.649">Sad</span><span begin="01:50.649" end="01:51.514">ness</span> <span begin="01:51.919" end="01:52.062">does</span><span begin="01:52.062" end="01:52.277">n't</span> <span begin="01:52.277" end="01:53.739">stay</span> <span begin="01:53.739" end="01:54.479">for</span> <span begin="01:54.479" end="01:55.817">long</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哀愁从不长留</span></p><p begin="01:56.921" end="02:01.147" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:56.921" end="01:57.109">E</span><span begin="01:57.109" end="01:57.325">very</span><span begin="01:57.325" end="01:58.402">thing</span> <span begin="01:58.402" end="01:59.259">just</span> <span begin="01:5